<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{% block title %}My Site{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootswatch@5.3.2/dist/lux/bootstrap.min.css">
    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog#">MySite</a>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
            <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
              <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/en/enhome">Home</a></li>
              <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/en/eninformation">Learn More</a></li>
              <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/en/enCV">Resume</a></li>
              <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/en/enEportfolio">E-portfolio</a></li>
              <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/blog/fr/Eportfolio">FR</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <main class="container mt-4">
      {% block body %}
      <div class="container my-5">

    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">My E-Portfolio</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center mb-5">Here is my E-portfolio</p>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>Description</h2>
        <p>Here are the critical skills acquired during my journey.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2>Critical skills</h2>

        <!-- Critical skills block 1 -->
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">AC11.02 Understand the architecture and foundations of digital systems, the principles of information coding, communications and the Internet</h3>
                <p class="card-text">In this learning, the goal is to understand a digital system.</p>
                
                <!-- Feelings -->
                <div class="mt-3 mb-3">
                    <h5>My feelings and positioning</h5>
                    <p>I consider that I have well acquired the expected basics for this skill.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Buttons -->
                <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/15mnCg5NomCo8cHnBrEaLRBNuB4z7HbPigJx3_7gyDYM/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.79zyscas4ezb" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Reflective analysis</a>
                <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1T7UPlDQaa5WCXquDHogZmhpZHoR_K_PBf5RdSQYlLf0/edit?tab=t.0" class="btn btn-secondary">Proof document</a>
            </div>
        </div>



        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">AC11.03: Configure the basic functions of the local network</h3>
                <p class="card-text">In this learning, the goal is to know how to configure the basics of a network.</p>

                <div class="mt-3 mb-3">
                    <h5>My feelings and positioning</h5>
                    <p>I liked working on this skill despite some difficulties.</p>
                </div>

                <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Xj01jG1sJFYxRMf4YkrNdN11p5h_kw9dSH1ukkh40h8/edit?tab=t.0" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Reflective analysis</a>
                <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/11u88FJLN-KQUvPDy39HkSn0l-RsHpWnYQO_wkyh9064/edit?tab=t.0" class="btn btn-secondary">Proof document</a>
            </div>
        </div>



        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">AC11.04 Master the roles and fundamental principles of operating systems in order to interact with them for configuring and administering networks and services provided</h3>
                <p class="card-text">This skill contributes to the creation and configuration of virtual client workstations, understanding what an OS is and the consequences of cyberattacks and how to protect against them, learning different protocols of the OSI model, and analyzing frames.</p>

                <div class="mt-3 mb-3">
                    <h5>My feelings and positioning</h5>
                    <p>I liked working on this skill and I have made good progress in this area.</p>
                </div>

                <a href="/analyse-reflective-2" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Reflective analysis</a>
                <a href="/document-preuve-2" class="btn btn-secondary">Proof document</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="height: 30px;"></div>


    <section>
      <h2>My feelings and positioning</h2>
        <p>The BUT RT suits me perfectly because it corresponds to my professional aspirations and my interest in IT development.</p>
      </section>
  </section>
    <div style="height: 30px;"></div>
  </div>
      {% endblock %}
    </main>

    <!-- Pied de page -->
    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3 mt-4">
      <p>&copy; 2026 - MonSite. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </footer>

    {% block javascripts %}
      {% block importmap %}
        {{ importmap('app') }}
      {% endblock %}
    {% endblock %}
  </body>
</html>
